{"opinion":{"isContribuable":false,"votes_total":25,"arguments_yes_count":0,"arguments_no_count":1,"id":511,"created_at":"2015-10-10T11:45:37+0200","updated_at":"2015-10-10T11:45:37+0200","body":"<p>Le mandataire judiciaire charg&eacute; d&#39;&eacute;valuer une soci&eacute;t&eacute; en difficult&eacute; &eacute;volue le patrimoine &laquo; savoir &raquo; de l&#39;entreprise en termes de logiciels, m&eacute;thodes de travail, formules, techniques de fabrication, brevets d&eacute;tenus, etc.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p>Le juge pronon&ccedil;ant la liquidation &eacute;value la pertinence de verser, aux communs, ce patrimoine, afin qu&#39;il ne soit pas perdu et qu&#39;il b&eacute;n&eacute;fice &agrave; d&#39;autres acteurs.<\/p>","versions_count":0,"sources_count":0,"arguments_count":1,"author":{"username":"Bernard Martinez","displayName":"Bernard Martinez","uniqueId":"bernardmartinez","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/bernardmartinez","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}},"type":{"id":90,"title":"Section 1","subtitle":"Les Communs","voteWidgetType":2,"votesHelpText":"Pensez-vous que cette proposition permet d'atteindre les objectifs pr\u00e9sent\u00e9s dans l\u2019explication de l\u2019article ?","commentSystem":2,"color":"blue","versionable":true,"sourceable":true,"votesThreshold":null,"votesThresholdHelpText":null},"sources":[],"arguments":[{"isContribuable":false,"id":2943,"body":"Disponible seulement en France avec FAI fran\u00e7ais. Autant en profiter dans notre pays qui supporte les co\u00fbts de la liquidation (ch\u00f4meurs, etc...)","created_at":"2015-10-10T14:54:58+0200","updated_at":"2015-10-10T14:54:58+0200","is_enabled":true,"votes_count":1,"type":0,"is_trashed":false,"author":{"username":"Jeanne Varasco","displayName":"Jeanne Varasco","uniqueId":"jeannevarasco","isAdmin":false,"media":{"url":"\/media\/cache\/default_avatar\/default\/0001\/01\/139_default_